src: "E dau dredre me kilai na ivakatakilakila taumada ni dementia. E levu na mate e rawa ni vakavuna eso na ivakatakilakila ni mate e via tautauvata kei na dementia. E levu vei ira na mate oqori era rawa ni qaravi. E bibi gona mo raica vakatotolo na nomu vuniwai se vakailesilesi ni tabana ni bula kevaka ko lomaleqataka."
ref: "The early signs and symptoms of dementia can be hard to notice. Many illnesses can cause dementia-like symptoms. Some of these illnesses are treatable. That is why you should see your doctor or health care provider if you are worried."

src:
"This is the most common form of dementia. Around two-thirds of people
with dementia have Alzheimers disease. Changes seen in the brain include
shrinkage and a build-up of abnormal proteins (plaques and tangles)."
ref:
"Oqo na matatali dementia e dau yaco vakalevu. E rauta ni rua na ikatolu vei
ira na tauvi dementia era Alzheimers. Kunei ni sa lailai sobu na mona oka
kina na kena tubucake na protein vakatubu mate (plagues and tangles)."
hyp: "Oqo na mataqali dementia e dau laurai vakalevu duadua. E rauta ni rua vei na tolu na lewenivanua era vakilai ena dementia era tauvimate ena mate ni Alzheimer. Na veiveisau e laurai ena mona e wili kina na kena vakamami lailai kei na kena kumuni na protein sega ni rairai vakaidina (plaques kei na tangles)."
